    "The rest of this article is organized as follows: Sect. 2 briefly introduces the background of 3D point clouds, including the acquisition, development, and applications of 3D point clouds, etc.",
    "Sections 3 to 6 respectively introduce the four categories of 3D-PCPR methods, namely feature-based, projection-based, segment-based, and multimodal-based methods, as shown in Fig. 1.",
    "Section 7 describes the main datasets, evaluation metrics and performance comparisons commonly used in 3D-PCPR.",
    "Section 8 introduces related applications of 3D-PCPR.",
    "Particularly, we discuss the future promising research directions of 3D-PCPR technology."
